# Activity Diagrams

## Facility Search Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User visits Facility Explorer] --> B[Enter search query]
    B --> C[Select facility types]
    C --> D[Select county]
    D --> E{Filter facilities}
    E -->|No results| F[Show empty state]
    E -->|Has results| G[Display filtered facilities]
    G --> H[Map updates with markers]
    H --> I[User clicks facility marker]
    I --> J[Show facility popup]
    J --> K[User can continue filtering]
    K --> B
```

## Command Center Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User visits Command Center] --> B[Load facility data]
    B --> C[Initialize map]
    C --> D[Display coverage zones]
    D --> E[Display medical deserts]
    E --> F[Show statistics]
    F --> G[User toggles auto-read]
    G -->|On| H[Enable auto-refresh]
    G -->|Off| I[Manual refresh only]
    H --> J[Auto-update every N seconds]
    I --> K[User clicks refresh]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Update map and stats]
```

## Map Interaction Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Map loads] --> B[User scrolls/zooms]
    B --> C[Leaflet handles zoom/pan]
    C --> D[User clicks marker]
    D --> E[Show popup]
    E --> F[User views facility details]
    F --> G[User closes popup]
    G --> B
```
